@@ -49,0 +49,7 @@
+# Canonicalize for riscv64 which autoconf-config.sub doesn't handle
+if echo $* | grep '^riscv64-linux' >/dev/null ; then
+    result=`echo $@ | sed 's/^riscv64-linux/riscv64-unknown-linux/'`
+    echo $result
+    exit
+fi
+
